<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #d32f2f;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .security-alert {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <h2>⚠️ Banking System - Security Alert</h2>
    </div>
    <div class='content'>
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>We detected an important security event on your account.</p>

      <div class='security-alert'>
        <h3>Security Event:</h3>
        <p>{{event}}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
      </div>

      <p><strong>If this was not you, please contact us immediately or change
          your password.</strong></p>
      <p>For your security, we recommend enabling two-factor authentication if
        you haven't already.</p>
    </div>
    <div class='footer'>
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Banking System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>